name: Discount Lasers Pointer Product Systems
overview: DiscountLasers.com offers all kinds of laser items and laser-related products at very affordable prices. We have a wide array of laser pens and pointers available in different colors from trusted manufacturers. Our line of products also include printers, levels, rangefinders, thermometers, laser tags and studfinders. DiscountLasers.com is your one-stop shop for all your day-to-day laser needs. Store owner, Theo Mayman, is an engineering graduate who is into hi-tech gadgets and likes playing video games during his free time. He has a collection of video game consoles, the oldest of which is a second generation Atari 2600 which he used to play with as a kid. He owns a Dalmatian named Jack, named after the lead character from a famous pirate movie. Jack lives in a doghouse which Theo designed himself. Theo plays the guitar and listens to alternative rock and acoustic music. He dreams of opening his own engineering firm someday and is working hard to achieve that goal.
